Richards Bay Sees 2011 Coal Shipments Little Changed From 2010

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-06-21T09:39:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-21/richards-bay-coal-terminal-may-ship-similar-volumes-to-last-year-ceo-says.html
Richards Bay Coal Terminal may ship
a similar volume of coal this year to last year when it exported
63.4 million metric tons, Raymond Chirwa, chief executive
officer of the terminal, said in a speech at the Coaltrans
conference in Johannesburg today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Carli Lourens at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net  